data.description: You will fall in love with this meticulously maintained home on a corner lot nestled in the heart of the Tuscany neighborhood in Evans! Boasting 5 bedrooms including a secluded primary space, this home will check all the boxes for your wants and needs! This home boasts an open layout with vaulted ceilings, hardwood floors, and built-ins providing tons of character! The kitchen features gorgeous updated cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and ample counter and storage space perfectly utilized for maximum impact. The living space and dining area are open to make it the ideal flow for entertaining. The primary retreat is a true haven of peace and rest allowing you the opportunity to rejuvenate from the burdens of the day: the ensuite bathroom offers dual sinks and plenty of counter space. Rounding out the main floor are 2 additional bedrooms, a full bathroom and a laundry room. The partially finished basement has living space, 2 bedrooms and framing ready for you to add another bathroom for immediate equity! You will appreciate the expansive backyard with the private, covered patio and large yard, offering additional entertaining space for friends or family. This home is perfectly situated with easy access to Route 85 & 34, making it a 15 minute drive to downtown Greeley. Enjoy the accessibility to enjoy the outdoors with a 5-10 minute walk to multiple neighborhood parks and a 5 minute drive to the Gateway Lakes Natural Area. Only a 5 min drive to a nearby shopping center with multiple shopping options including grocery. Call for your private showing today!
